# The [[crime]] of [[break in|breaking into]] a [[vehicle]], [[house]], [[store]], or other enclosure with the [[intent]] to [[steal]].
# {{legal}} Under the [[common law]], [[breaking and entering]] of the [[dwelling]] of another [[at night]] with the intent to [[commit]] a [[felony]].
# {{context|legal|US}} Under the [[w:Model Penal Code|Model Penal Code]], entering a [[building]] or [[occupied]] [[structure]] with [[purpose]] to commit a [[crime]] therein, unless the premises are at the time open to the public. Model Penal Code § 221.1.

